*[[File:en/Manual/Base Set/Trains/Lev2cyclops.png|Lev2 'Cyclops']] [[es/Manual/Base Set/Trains/Lev2 'Cyclops'|Lev2 'Cyclops']]
*[[File:en/Manual/Base Set/Trains/Lev3pegasus.png|Lev3 'Pegasus']] [[es/Manual/Base Set/Trains/Lev3 'Pegasus'|Lev3 'Pegasus']]
*[[File:en/Manual/Base Set/Trains/Lev4chimaerarhead.png|Lev4 'Chimaera']] [[es/Manual/Base Set/Trains/Lev4 'Chimaera'|Lev4 'Chimaera']]
Y la única locomotora MagLev en el escenario Fantasía es:
*[[File:en/Manual/Base Set/Trains/Wizzowowrocketeer.png|Wizzowow Rocketeer]] [[es/Manual/Base Set/Trains/Wizzowow Rocketeer|Wizzowow Rocketeer]]

